content.webTitle: Fulham v Manchester United: Squad sheets

fields.headline: Fulham v Manchester United: Squad sheets
fields.bodyText: Martin Jol insists he is not feeling the pressure as Fulham supporters grumble about their team's shoddy form. But he must know that a repeat of last week's abject display at Southampton could lead to a severe beating at the hands of Manchester United. The visitors may not have found their groove yet this season, either, but an away win still seems the most likely outcome.
